    {"type":"text","id":"conflict_detail","x":615,"y":185,"width":230,"height":210,"text":"Temperature: 0\u2013100 gauge\nwith natural decay over time\n\n5 Trigger Types\n  jealousy \u00b7 boundary testing\n  emotional \u00b7 power struggle\n  neglect\n\n3 Escalation Levels\n  subtle \u2192 direct \u2192 crisis\n\n4 Conflict States\n  passive-aggressive \u00b7 cold\n  vulnerable \u00b7 explosive\n\nGottman Four Horsemen\ndetection for patterns","originalText":"Temperature: 0\u2013100 gauge\nwith natural decay over time\n\n5 Trigger Types\n  jealousy \u00b7 boundary testing\n  emotional \u00b7 power struggle\n  neglect\n\n3 Escalation Levels\n  subtle \u2192 direct \u2192 crisis\n\n4 Conflict States\n  passive-aggressive \u00b7 cold\n  vulnerable \u00b7 explosive\n\nGottman Four Horsemen\ndetection for patterns","fontSize":10,"fontFamily":1,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#be123c","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":11054,"version":1,"versionNonce":11055,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.25}
